    "description": "Ono Sokki Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells measuring instruments in Japan and internationally. It operates through measuring instruments and custom-made test equipment segments. The company provides laboratory automation, automotive test system, and automotive measurement and analysis tools, such as sensors / measurement equipment, GPS speedometer, combustion analysis system, and sound and vibration analysis system; sound and vibration, torque measurement, flow rate measurement, rpm & speed measurement, and dimensional measurement devices; and data processing & signal analysis products. It also offers custom-made testing equipment for research and development and quality control purposes; consulting services; cloud services related to sound and vibration; after-sales services; and engineering services. In addition, the company engages in non-life insurance agency business; management of land, buildings and equipment, as well as provides other contracted services. Ono Sokki Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1940 and is headquartered in Yokohama, Japan."
